                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2899-18431023 t18431023-2899-punishment-70"></join>Confined Two Years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Third Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</hi>
